name: Laura Pietrzykowski
title: Realtor
body: Deena you are my life saver! Would not be able to survive without you!

name: Malaika Hunt
title: Broker Associate
body: Deena is great to work with!  She is responsive and goes above and beyond to get our escrows closed.  I highly recommend Deena to any of my colleagues.

name: Claudia Soto
title: Realtor
body: Working with Deena as TC makes my job much easier as she follows up immediately. She takes ownership and follows up from beginning to end. Her professionalism and knowledge is outstanding. She always goes above and beyond, I have the confidence knowing that the job was well done and in a timely manner. She is part of my business success. Thank you Deena!!

name: Randa Peterson
title: Realtor
body: I was looking for a new Transaction Coordinator and Deena came highly recommended. Right from the beginning Deena was on top of everything. The transaction went smoothly and I can't figure out why I didn't make a move earlier. Deena is the BEST!!
